Package rbadia.voidspace.model

Class Summary
Asteroid Represents every asteroid that fall in the screen.
Bullet Represents a bullet fired by a ship.
EnemyBullet Represents the bullets fired by the enemy-ship.
EnemyShip Represents an enemy-ship that attacks to the point where the ship is located in the instant it appears.
Item Represents the items that will fall from when an multiple-life asteroid is destroyed.
KamikazeShip Represents the kamikaze enemy-ship which attacks the player without being destroyed.
Ship Represents a ship/space craft.
Star Star Class used to represent a star Star are actually drawn like a like with length 1 but this object stores their speed established randomly on construction
